# ⚖️ 6. RIP vs OSPF (VERY IMPORTANT)

| Feature    | RIP             | OSPF       |
| ---------- | --------------- | ---------- |
| Type       | Distance Vector | Link State |
| Metric     | Hop Count       | Cost       |
| Speed      | Slow            | Fast       |
| Max Hops   | 15              | Unlimited  |
| Efficiency | Low             | High       |

